News : Nouveau Local :) New Office :)

New Office
​@ "les Grands Voisins"

[EN | FR] Paris 14th, March 2, 2016. I have moved into the "Mon Premier Bureau" incubator at 72 ave Denfert-Rochereau in the new private neighborhood "les Grands voisins," a disaffected 17th-century hospital Saint Vincent de Paul. The community here glows with meaning! There are a multitude of artists of all sorts, artisans, non-profits including Aurore who runs the place, temporary housing, training rooms, workshops, services for migrant minors, even a local radio "Libre à toi," and a coffee-shop cultural center "la Lingerie" that would be a jewel in any American campus. Nature even celebrated the day with snow-flake confetti (see photos).
